# Copy to .dev.vars for local dev. NEVER commit real values.
#
# R2 SQL bearer token. Create at: Cloudflare dashboard -> R2 -> Manage R2 API tokens.
# Required scopes (open-beta quirk: Storage Admin R&W is required even for
# read-only SQL): R2 Storage (Admin Read & Write) + R2 Data Catalog (Read &
# Write) + R2 SQL (Read).
# Production: npx wrangler secret put R2_SQL_TOKEN
R2_SQL_TOKEN=""
